<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: #0f1419;
      color: #e7e9ea;
    }
    .wrap {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 28rem;
    }
    .code {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      color: #1d9bf0;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #8b98a5;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .path {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      word-break: break-all;
      color: #71767b;
    }
    a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      color: #1d9bf0;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="code">404</p>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <p>요청하신 주소에 해당하는 페이지가 없습니다.</p>
    <% if (typeof path !== 'undefined' && path) { %>
      <p class="path"><%= path %></p>
    <% } %>
    <a href="/">홈으로</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>